???"This grimoire was dropped by a monster while I was being chased
and running away. It's probably a grimoire that can be stolen. The

so it's quite valuable."

???"Uh, me? I'm an archaeologist who loves sweet and sour pork
bento."

Becky: "Hah... Aren't you that old man from the desert? We've talked
once before, remember?"
Old Man"Ah...! That's right. It's been a while, hasn't it?"

Becky: "Seriously, who would've thought a sweet and sour pork bento
vendor would come to a place like this. What kind of information
magazine is this?"

Old Man"Well, that's because it's the phantom sweet and sour pork
bento vendor, always on the run from customers. Only those who find it
can taste its supreme deliciousness!"

Becky: "Got it, got it. We don't have time to mess around with dirty
old men. See ya."
